Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:40.51,eptitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HEBE1D2&\pos(320,150)}Miracle Girls #26\NI'm going to change schools
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:01:59.53,Default,Yamagishi,0000,0000,0000,,What a play, Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:03.25,Default,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,We can win this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:05.77,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Ryoko, it's too bad you can't play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:09.79,Default,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh this? It's okay, I'll get well before the final.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.83,0:02:12.70,Default,Yamagishi,0000,0000,0000,,Our school will make the final?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:13.89,Default,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.55,0:02:19.74,Default,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay because Tomomi is on my team.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.76,0:02:20.50,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:28.54,Default,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.77,0:02:31.92,Default,player,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi nice block!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.94,0:02:32.93,Default,player,0000,0000,0000,,You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:35.30,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a fluke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:49.78,Default,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Number One extra player in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:51.68,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,See I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:01.56,Default,Takeda,0000,0000,0000,,You are Matsunaga Tomomi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.56,0:03:02.71,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.38,0:03:05.77,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, what can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:09.08,Default,Takeda,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Takeda, from Kanaria Jogakuin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:16.01,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Kanaria? ... The favorite for the championship?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:21.43,Default,Takeda,0000,0000,0000,,Matsunaga Tomomi, you've been scouted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:22.75,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,What??!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:28.25,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:31.72,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh I'm so hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:34.01,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,You can eat that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:38.31,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:41.89,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you know I'm making food for Kurashige-sempai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:47.92,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I made it for you and really put my heart into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.38,0:03:51.59,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,That's a cute cookie, it looks as if it were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.97,0:03:54.34,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such things, it's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:55.72,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,It's a wonderful cookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:56.95,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:59.08,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna be a good wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:00.30,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:08.46,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be tough for senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.49,0:04:09.69,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:13.68,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:16.34,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,By the way Tomomi, how was the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:19.98,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey listen, I was scouted!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:21.55,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:27.37,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean what? You know volleyball, I was scouted for volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:29.98,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,What was Tomomi scout?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:36.79,Default,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! A scout had been watching her since the first round.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:40.01,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:46.25,Default,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it? It's Kanajo, that school is the best place to play volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:54.52,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,A scholarship and you don't need to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:57.02,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,That means, all you have to do is play volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:05:00.23,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:05.88,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Well that's good. Kanajo's volleyball team is the best team in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:08.02,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna go there Tomomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:10.74,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,No way, I don't have any intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:16.27,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, you don't wanna separate with somebody, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:17.88,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:23.25,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,But finally Tomomi who has only reflexes has a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:25.82,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean only reflexes, don't say that, it's cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:27.86,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Because that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:31.16,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Ok, I made it. Cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:35.15,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, senpai will be happy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:38.83,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Those cookies aren't done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:43.34,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi! Why didn't you tell me earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:54.89,Default,student,0000,0000,0000,,I watched yesterday's game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:56.54,Default,student,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it next game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.03,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:06:01.01,Default,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,Morning Tomomi, Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:02.16,Default,Tomo&Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:03.58,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,How is your arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:08.35,Default,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting better. I can take off the cast soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:12.84,Default,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, congratulations, you were scouted by Kanajo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:15.30,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,What? How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:20.02,Default,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,You can't have any secrets from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:21.26,Default,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:26.82,Default,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,Actually I heard from my coach, I was so happy that I told everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:30.77,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:32.48,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:42.16,Default,Yamagishi,0000,0000,0000,,A future Olympian has appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:52.16,Default,Yamagishi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey everybody, I'm now gonna interview Matsunaga Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:57.19,Default,Yamagishi,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody please be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:07:07.54,Default,Yamagishi,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}How do you feel now, as Kanajo is a regular\N championship contender famous nationwide?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:11.87,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't decided if I'm gonna go or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:15.42,Default,Yamagishi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she is very modest. Just like a champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:18.11,Default,Yamagishi,0000,0000,0000,,She is truly the future's superstar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:35.65,Default,fan,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Tomomi you're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:38.59,Default,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:40.07,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.28,0:07:43.58,Default,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, talk about popularity!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:49.32,Default,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,You are truly very popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:52.06,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't nice to my teammates.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:57.17,Default,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,No way, they're so happy from their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:08:01.45,Default,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,Also, it encourages them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:02.91,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Ryoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:04.42,Default,coach,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Matsunaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:05.19,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:09.50,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Takeda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:15.69,Default,coach,0000,0000,0000,,Okay Matsunaga, listen to him very carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:16.60,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:19.31,Default,Takeda,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much because I know you are busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:22.21,Default,coach,0000,0000,0000,,Oh that's okay, I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:33.43,Default,Takeda,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I came here so suddenly, I feel rather hurried.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:40.04,Default,Takeda,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you think about that last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.34,0:08:45.87,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}Are you sure you want to scout me? There are\N so many players who are better than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:48.89,Default,Takeda,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one I want, Matsunaga!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.15,0:09:03.03,Default,Takeda,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, now there are many players better than you, but I believe you have potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:06.16,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Potential, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:10.68,Default,Takeda,0000,0000,0000,,Please come to my school. I will make you a world class player.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:13.56,Default,Takeda,0000,0000,0000,,Surely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:29.72,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:38.53,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Noda!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:41.22,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Noda!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:44.71,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:50.38,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing special, but I wanna talk about Kanajo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:57.76,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Oh that thing. Now you wanna be great at the dash too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:09:59.00,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:03.53,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,I better practice hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.90,0:10:05.25,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:09.57,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,I've always know about your reflexes, you're a natural at volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:18.47,Default,student,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Noda, why don't you date after club?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:20.82,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:23.54,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,See you Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:26.78,Default,student,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:29.93,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, it'll be worse than losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:32.79,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Noda...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:57.19,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:17.71,Default,Yamagishi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:18.49,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:23.24,Default,Yamagishi,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Tomomi is truly great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:26.57,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. We've gotta work harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:27.93,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Noda!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:32.27,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright about spending all your time here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:34.17,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:38.36,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi went to Kanaria Jogakuin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.41,0:12:00.41,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:03.36,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to make you decide so suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.69,0:12:07.53,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,It's because they're so well equipped and treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:09.35,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:15.41,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm sure. Takeda said he'll believe in my potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:20.99,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,The formal procedure will be after the final, but I'm gonna come here as soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:24.91,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, are you really sure? Did you talk to Noda?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:28.03,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't involve Noda.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:29.60,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I've already decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:31.19,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:45.06,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, I've gotta clean my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:49.63,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:55.98,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I feel nostalgia for my junior high school uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.07,0:13:00.03,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:03.36,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you Mikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:08.11,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi. Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.59,0:13:09.67,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:13.03,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi please exchange my school for your school!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:14.72,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:18.05,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Sport's festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:24.03,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I was chosen as a relay athlete.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:25.38,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:28.86,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,So please. It's my wish for my whole life...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.63,0:13:31.72,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Please participate in the relay instead of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.01,0:13:32.95,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:37.59,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, a perfect fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:39.78,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:41.80,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about Tomomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:43.19,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:45.81,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, nobody'll ever find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:47.52,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:55.17,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I know I've asked you to do such a rash thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:56.59,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:14:01.99,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,But Noda will be participating in the class match relay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:03.00,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Noda?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:07.05,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,If I was last he'd pick on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:11.15,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:12.39,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.69,0:14:13.53,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:15.24,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:17.34,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:24.28,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,See, you're just like me. That's me from anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:27.14,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,You're so well prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:31.63,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Please remember my school friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:41.57,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Ack! This guy! That's Noda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:49.04,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,This dummy's full of energy because he's the cheerleader.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:51.56,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,It ticks me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:53.53,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,He looks fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:58.94,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk to him as he's a monster, devil, and my own personal waterloo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:14.33,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,My coed school has so many guys. I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:15.96,Default,student,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning Matsunaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:17.57,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,G-good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.36,0:15:19.83,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.48,0:15:42.89,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}Wow! This is the first time I'm seeing a men's\N basketball game, everything's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:50.69,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,That guy is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:54.86,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,His jumping and running is the best, and the ball looks like it's glued to his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:15:59.15,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,And he looks like he's enjoying himself so much!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:05.18,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,To the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:12.28,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:13.78,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:32.83,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,That guy is Noda Yuuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:39.14,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Mikage, how do you solve this question?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:42.64,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,That question is solved like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:45.53,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,That's great. You are a genius girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:46.87,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,How about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:51.32,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you to study so hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:55.64,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I wanna enter the Arudia Fuzoku school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:58.79,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go to the same school as Noda does.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.84,0:17:00.80,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What? Noda?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:05.29,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't read my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:22.33,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:28.36,Default,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:30.13,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Ryoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.24,0:17:33.25,Default,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,This is it, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:41.02,Default,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little bit sad you're changing schools, but we're friends even separated, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:42.53,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:44.72,Default,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:46.75,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:56.43,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,It's great that Tomomi was scouted by Kanajo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:18:00.12,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:05.97,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi was saying she wouldn't change schools but then she suddenly changed her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:09.08,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,She might have some problem with Noda.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:12.96,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,That guy, he probably doesn't even realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.37,0:18:16.76,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:55.69,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.59,0:19:03.97,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:08.30,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really sure it's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:15.46,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything, because I've already done the formal procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:18.90,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,You've forgotten something you've gotta do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:26.34,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Meet Noda.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:38.99,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Noda.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:45.26,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,That was where the results of the exams were announced.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.99,0:19:55.50,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I found it, it's over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:57.91,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:20:02.60,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. We're in the same school as of April.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:25.76,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:28.97,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna transfer schools seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:34.94,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Because you agreed with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:38.71,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say you had to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.12,0:20:41.42,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,But you said play volleyball seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:45.45,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! You can do volleyball seriously even here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:10.61,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:12.30,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:19.22,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Noda.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:23.73,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway I like my school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:34.76,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:52.58,Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,We got a triple play!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:54.64,Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,How come Noda's so hyper?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.64,0:21:56.95,Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,He's the temporary coach for little league.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.95,0:21:59.82,Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,I see, we help him with new magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.92,0:22:01.30,Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Miracle Girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.30,0:22:02.61,Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,"Miracle by baseball."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.68,0:22:04.58,Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,We wanna give you a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:09.47,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:09.47,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna toki mo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.59,0:22:12.76,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.59,0:22:12.76,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Futari janakya dame nano
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.68,0:22:16.10,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we had a fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.68,0:22:16.10,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenka shite mo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.35,0:22:19.31,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.35,0:22:19.31,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Futari janakya dame nano
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.19,0:22:35.95,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,There are days when kindness is so close
