Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:52.76,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we know it better than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:45.84,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Honto wa dare yori mo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.96,0:22:52.76,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Wakkate iru noni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.30,0:22:59.19,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,When we can't say "I'm sorry,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.30,0:22:59.19,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Gomenne to ienai toki wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.27,0:23:06.23,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,we send out feelings through the little fingers.
